Subject: [PATCH 0/7] KVM: x86: Conditional Hyper-V emulation enablement
Date: Wed, 13 Jan 2021 15:37:14 +0100
Message-Id: <20210113143721.328594-1-vkuznets@redhat.com>
MIME-Version: 1.0
X-Scanned-By: MIMEDefang 2.79 on 10.5.11.16
